&lt;p&gt;University College London Hospital are looking forSurgical SHO&#39;s to join the Bank in the following departments;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;GI Surgery&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Urology&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;T&amp;O&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Head &amp; Neck&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Essential Requirements;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Right to work in the UK&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full GMC Registration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A minimum of 6 months experience working within the NHS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in General Surgery and/or all other surgical specialties (ENT, T&amp;O, Urology, GI)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Bank Locums are invaluable to us and in return for their diligence andcommitment, we offer the following benefits:-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunities to work across sites, gaining invaluable knowledge and experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sites in great central London locations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive Locum bank pay rates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Priority of shifts over agency workers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A professional Locum Recruitment Team that will ensure you are registered and compliant to work shifts as soon as possible&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A dedicated compliance team that will ensure you remain compliant to work, sending out regular expiry updates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An online self-booking system and attentive bookings team, accommodating your convenience and availability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Electronic Timesheet submission&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Onsite office and designated Business Partners to offer daily support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Our own Training Academy offering free annual Mandatory Training updates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
